item.description:
@Pest wrote:

[quote=“Soulcist, post:8, topic:549980”][quote author=wimstr link=topic=668856.msg4473322#msg4473322 date=1424359240]

I would probably never play this because of two reasons…

  1. Get-Boned… I’ve seen some names before, but this…
  2. “LOOKING FOR STAFF,” the most alluring thing anyone can put in the title of an advertisement; unfortunately, it attracts the wrong players.

Agreed with this.
[/quote]
Pretty much. I’m going to assume that you’re either new to the scene or in a funny kind of mood? For sure, this is RSPS but at least have some pride of what your name is going to be on or going to run lol.

Either or, good luck with the server.[/quote]
i did change the server name lol.
